《'''为什么现在统治世界的是西方'''》（{{lang-en|''Why the West Rules—For Now''}}）为[[美国|美国]][[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]的历史学教授{{link-en|伊恩·莫里斯|Ian Morris (historian)}}的著作，2010年10月12日由{{link-en|法勒、施特劳斯和吉鲁出版社|Farrar, Straus and Giroux}}出版。该书比较了将[[中國文化史|中國文化史]]和[[印度文化圈|南亚]]划为东方，将欧美和中东划为[[西方|西方]]，并比较了这两者15000年的历史进程。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.stanford.edu/news/2010/september/morris-west-rules-091410.html |title=Stanford historian tells why the West rules - for now |access-date=2015-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150902193817/http://news.stanford.edu/news/2010/september/morris-west-rules-091410.html |archive-date=2015-09-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该书获得2011年{{link-en|国际笔会美国中心文学非小说写作奖决选作品|PEN Center USA}}，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://penusa.org/2011-literary-awards-festival-winners|title=THE 2011 LITERARY AWARD WINNERS|publisher={{tsl|en|PEN Center USA||PEN Center USA}}|date=|accessdate=2014-08-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120714031530/http://penusa.org/2011-literary-awards-festival-winners|archivedate=2012-07-14}}</ref> 2011{{link-en|益得书摘国际图书奖|GetAbstract International Book Award}}等书奖，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.getabstract.com/en/pages/web/BookAward.jsp|title=getAbstract International Book Award|publisher={{tsl|en|getAbstract||getAbstract}}|date=|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705065546/http://www.getabstract.com/en/pages/web/BookAward.jsp|archive-date=2014-07-05|dead-url=no}}</ref> 并荣登《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.newsweek.com/21-ways-be-smarter-2011-66765|title=21 Ways to Be Smarter in 2011|publisher=''[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]''|date=2011-01-03|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826113429/http://www.newsweek.com/21-ways-be-smarter-2011-66765|archive-date=2014-08-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[外交政策_(杂志)|外交政策]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/11/28/the_global_thinkers_20_most_recommended_books?page=0,1|title=The Global Thinkers' Book Club|publisher=''[[外交政策_(杂志)|外交政策 (杂志)]]''|date=2011-11-28|accessdate=2014-08-24|author=Kedar Pavgi|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131120091014/http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/11/28/the_global_thinkers_20_most_recommended_books?page=0,1|archivedate=2013-11-20}}</ref>《[[外交_(杂志)|外交]]》、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ianmorris.org/docs/review-whythewest-foreignaffairs.pdf|title=Review: Why the West Rules--For Now|publisher=Ian Morris's website|date=|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514182332/http://www.ianmorris.org/docs/review-whythewest-foreignaffairs.pdf|archive-date=2013-05-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》等年度荐书，以13种语言版本發行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.economist.com/node/17199546?story_id=17199546&fsrc=rss|title=Global power: On top of the world|publisher=''[[经济学人|经济学人]]''|date=2010-10-07|accessdate=2014-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140810231751/http://www.economist.com/node/17199546?story_id=17199546&fsrc=rss|archive-date=2014-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>

